author: reanderson13
title: Woman Found Dead In Washington Heights
text:
NEW YORK (CBSNewYork) — Police were called to Washington Heights on Saturday afternoon where they found a woman unconscious and unresponsive.
Officers discovered the woman just before 1:30 p.m. near West 187 Street and Chittenden Avenue.
EMS responded and she was pronounced dead at the scene.
Police said the investigation is ongoing.
